// Settings UI generated by OpenAI Codex under the direction of the project owner.
//
// The settings surface deliberately uses only standard WinForms containers and
// controls. It is a long-lived editor with native TextBox, Label, LinkLabel,
// and Button children; mixing those with a fully extended DWM client frame or
// custom UserPaint cards is not a reliable .NET Framework rendering path.

